    <preface>
      <p><span style="color:#000000"><b>INSTITUTE FOR APPRENTICESHIPS AND TECHNICAL EDUCATION (TRANSFER OF FUNCTIONS ETC) ACT 2025</b></span></p>
      <p><span style="color:#000000">EXPLANATORY NOTES</span></p>
    </preface>
    <mainBody>
      <toc>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes" level="1"><inline name="tocHeading">The whole Explanatory Note</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/1" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Overview of the Act</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/2" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Policy background</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/3" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">The case for Skills England</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/4" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Legal background</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/5" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Territorial extent and application</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2025/14/notes/section/6" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Commentary on provisions of the Act</inline></tocItem>
